longBusinessSummary: eEducation Albert AB (publ) develops and markets digital educational services on a subscription basis to private individuals and schools in Sweden and internationally. The company operates an application-based education platform for children aged 3-16 years. It offers various educational services to younger aged from 1-9 years, as well as older children in the age 10-16 years in subjects, such as Mathematics, English, Geography, Code, and Reading and Writing. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Gothenburg, Sweden.
